Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:05.93,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:08.64,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:13.81,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:18.94,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:31.71,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:40.13,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:52.02,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:55.27,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:58.07,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.11,0:01:02.90,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:08.41,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:17.71,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:05.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! I gotta take off this belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:12.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:17.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll just have to get used\Nto our security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:19.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:22.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:25.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:31.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:33.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I had a fight with\Nmy wife and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:41.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my kid is still small,\Nso it looks like I'll be commuting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:44.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You should live at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:46.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These rooms are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should move here\Nwith your whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lump me together\Nwith a carefree bachelor like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:56.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:03:00.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on a date, the three of them\Nare in Misa-Misa's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:03.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Surveillance cameras, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it can't be helped
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:09.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since we believe that Amane\Nmight be involved with second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:12.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Matsuda,\Nstop calling her Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:14.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't feel like a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:22.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay no attention to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:24.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, are you going to\Neat that piece of cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:27.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweets are fattening,\Nso I try not to eat them too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:28.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you can still eat sweets\Nwithout gaining weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:33.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're making fun\Nof me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:37.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you leave me\Nalone with Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:40.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I leave you two alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be watching with\Nthe surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:43.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:46.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert! Will you stop\Ndoing these sick things?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:49.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me whatever you like.\NI'm taking your cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:53.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'll just close the curtains\Nand turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We also have infrared cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing the subject...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:01.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite moving into fully\Nequipped headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't seem\Nvery enthusiastic, Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enthusiasm, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:10.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any...\NActually, I'm kind of depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:12.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:13.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:19.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time I thought\Nthat you were Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:23.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just shocked that\Nmy deduction was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:29.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm still suspicious of you,\Nhence these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:33.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira can control people's actions...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:39.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Kira was controlling you\Nto make me suspect that you were Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:43.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Misa were both\Ncontrolled by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:48.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about that,\Neverything matches up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:52.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By that reasoning,\NMisa and I were controlled,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but doesn't that still mean\Nthat we're Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:57.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I don't think I'm wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:07.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that when you were confined,\Nyou were Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:12.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And while you were confined,\Ncriminals stopped dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:16.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were Kira until then,\Nso it works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:19.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But after two weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:20.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira Returns\Ncriminals began dying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on that evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Kira's power can pass\Nfrom person to person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:31.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an interesting idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:35.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's true,\Nit won't be easy to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's why I'm at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:42.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we catch those under Kira's control,\NKira's powers will be passed on to others
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the former will have no memory\Nof their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that it's useless\Nto catch anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:51.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that hasn't been\Ndecided yet, right? Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:58.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.\NNo, it's better to not try so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:03.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our lives will be in danger if\Nwe desperately try to chase him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:09.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:28.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:32.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't feel like doing anything\Njust because I wasn't Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and because your\Ndeduction was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:37.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have phrased it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:41.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant it would be a waste for us\Nto make a move, so we shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:44.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can catch him\Nif we don't chase him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how many\Ninnocent people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you've involved in this case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:51.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, you're the one\Nwho confined Misa and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:57.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But whatever the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:20.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that my deduction was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact is, the case isn't\Ngoing to be solved simply as
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:25.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Light Yagami is Kira" and\N"Misa Amane is the Second Kira."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:28.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was a bit depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:31.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm human.\NAm I not allowed to feel like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:32.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:34.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:38.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's as if you won't be\Nsatisfied unless I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:41.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be satisfied\Nunless you're Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:47.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:51.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An eye...for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:01.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know\NI'm pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call the room and stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen, Ryuzaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-Misa is number one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:15.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in Eighteen Magazine's\Nreader popularity poll!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:17.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that it's been\Ndecided that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:22.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll be starring as the heroine in\Nthe next film by the director, Nishinaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda's acting stupid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Matsuda is a natural at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:37.48,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(418,0)}Two months later
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:45.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, I know you're not feeling up to it,\Nbut come over here for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it unbalanced?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:56.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of them were prominent\NJapanese businessmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:58.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They all died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, Yotsuba's stock prices\Nrose and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,those of other companies dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:07.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they are deaths\Nthat are in Yotsuba's favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Checking back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:12.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there've been as many as thirteen\Nsuch cases in the past three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:13.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:17.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only conclude that\NKira is supporting Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:21.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... But if that's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:24.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then punishing criminals\Nis not this Kira's true intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:28.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He's punishing criminals\Nas a front and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:32.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,killing people for\Nthe benefit of his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:35.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:37.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel a little\Nmore enthusiastic now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:53.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amusing how well this has gone,\Nwithout anyone suspecting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:58.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yotsuba's benefits and stock prices\Nhave been increasing slowly, but steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:02.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's all proceeding\Naccording to our calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:07.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just worried about one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:11.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the three people\Nwe decided to kill last week
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,die of heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:14.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we decided that one of them\Nwas going to die from an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably because
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:20.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we chose the accident to\Noccur on the Coastal Bay Route.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the appointed time,\Nhe wasn't at his home,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:26.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but had snuck off to Italy\Nwith a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:30.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nif the request is impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:34.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira kills the person by heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I told you last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:39.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you request only accidental deaths\Nand death by disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:42.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they're finished in a natural way\Nin the shortest amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:46.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the police should be\Ntoo busy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:48.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,investigating the deaths of criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:53.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone could trace the deaths\Nof those others back to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he would be a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:57.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we've already\Ntaken precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:04.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Oh, you too, Mogi!\NGreat job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With Light's help,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:11.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the theory that Kira is involved with\Nthe Yotsuba Group has become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:13.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:15.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:17.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably the case, Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:24.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just heard from the Director\Nthat Kira's offered bribes to politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the police\Ndon't chase him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:33.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he won't lay a hand on\Nany politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:38.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police caved in to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:39.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi has already made up\Nhis mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, Matsuda...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if you really still\Nwant to pursue Kira, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:53.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,turn in your letters of resignation\Nto the NPA with Mogi and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:58.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot pursue Kira anymore\Nunless you quit the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:07.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were told that we would be\Nfired if we were to pursue Kira with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:09.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, Chief, you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:12.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In a few hours,\NI'm no longer going to be your chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you all have your own lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:18.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please think hard before\Nyou make your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:23.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Especially those who are\Nmarried and have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:28.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you all should\Nremain police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was alone to begin with...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:35.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm grateful to all of you\Nfor sticking with me this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:38.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can do this by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to visit you all\Nat the police department
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:45.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and bring you Kira's head as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:49.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki! As long as I'm here,\Nyou won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:51.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:53.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:58.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have Light working\Nwith me until I catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:02.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone else should\Nremain police officers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:07.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you told us that you needed\Nthe help of the police in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because the police\Nas an organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:12.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't bow to Kira and\Nhoped to arrest him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:17.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really think the help\Nof two or three civilians
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who quit the police force can\Nreally count as the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the police have decided
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:25.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that they don't want to\Ncatch Kira, so that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:32.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true we wouldn't be of\Nmuch help not being police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:36.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about our feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:38.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've risked our lives to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:40.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We at least have the right to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:43.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,whether we stay here or\Nremain police officers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:45.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:48.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then decide which you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if you quit the police force,\Nyou'll be unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:58.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we catch Kira,\Nwhat are you going to do afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:00.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:05.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't thought about it,\Nbut after we catch Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:08.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll be looking\Nfor a job again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:11.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:14.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also going to quit the police\Nand chase Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have to do my job\Nas Misa-Misa's manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:20.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I remained a police officer,\NI'd feel like a loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what you say, Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:35.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about if I remained a police officer\Nand helped you in my spare time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:40.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you remain a police officer,\Nplease don't come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:43.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't leak information...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:45.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give you any information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:51.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As detectives,\Nyou are free to chase Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:55.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think it's right\Nto give up your livelihoods
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:59.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and harm your families\Njust to chase Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:02.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as Ryuzaki says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will blame you\Nif you quit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:08.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NNo one will think of you as a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:09.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:10.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a family, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:14.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our situations are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:17.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:23.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was prepared to\Ndie at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:28.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I quit here,\Nhow will I face Ukita...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:33.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Why can't a detective\Nworking for the police chase Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:35.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:41.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In case anything happened\Nto a member of the task force,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:44.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even if they were fired,\Nyou entrusted me to make preparations
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so that financial support would\Nbe offered to their families,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:51.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so that they would never be in need\Nfor the rest of their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:54.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you telling them that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:57.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what you say, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:15:59.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:03.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so our livelihood was secured?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad, Aizawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:16.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki... Were you watching to see\Nif I would quit the police to join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that, Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:22.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki just doesn't like to\Nsay things like that himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:25.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was testing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:31.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching to see\Nwhich you would choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:33.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:41.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll quit and\Nremain a police officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:42.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't make a decision quickly\Nlike you all and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was leaning towards staying\Na police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:51.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's become clear to me once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the way Ryuzaki\Ndoes everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:05.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also just can't stand
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:14.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,how he can say things like this\Nso shamelessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:15.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for\Nyour hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:31.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I found another.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:35.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The branch manager of\NYotsuba's biggest rival bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:39.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,died on September 7th when\Nhe slipped on the steps of his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,September 7th\Nwas a Friday...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I checked once more and discovered\Nthat the deaths
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:50.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that are beneficial to Yotsuba\Nare concentrated around the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:56.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, the times of death\Nwere random...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but gradually, they became concentrated
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:00.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,around Friday nights through\NSaturday afternoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:03.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing you noticed that, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:05.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you,\NI'm no longer the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:08.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you'll always be\Nthe Chief to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:11.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be some sort of hint, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't lost to you and Ryuzaki yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:18.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be dead weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:19.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead weight...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kira someone from Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:25.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is Kira using Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't figured that out yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:29.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but let's investigate this with\Nthe assumption that this is Kira's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:32.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's thoroughly investigate Yotsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:37.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've compiled a list of all domestic\Nemployees in the Yotsuba Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,300,000, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:43.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you compiled\Nthe list so quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Mr. Mogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:48.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mogi's been amazing\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:50.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:54.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can do\Nbesides being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:58.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then could you get me\Nanother cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:04.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And for our guests over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:08.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they-?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:09.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When did they get in-?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They are our new members.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:20.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aiber. A con-man.\NPleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:23.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wedy. I'm a thief by trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:26.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A con-man and a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:27.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:31.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiber has excellent social skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:34.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a con-man who can\Ncozy up to our target.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use him for infiltrative investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:42.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wedy is a thief who can crack\Nany lock, safe, or security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:46.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof, she entered without\Nany of us noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:50.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be working together\Nwith criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:51.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:55.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but not the type who\Nwill surface and be killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:58.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of them as pros of\Nthe underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:03.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. If we want to investigate Yotsuba,\Nwe need people like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:06.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all work together and\Ngive it our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:08.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:09.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:23.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:24.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:25.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:27.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:29.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:30.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:33.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:36.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least tell me if you're coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:39.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't bought enough\Nfor your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you half of my croquette-!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:45.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I haven't had a break\Nfor quite a while now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I got some time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:49.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is a "time off" a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:51.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:52.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on,\NI can have a break every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:59.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can take you to this park...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:02.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,no, the zoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:05.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or even the amusement park...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:10.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:16.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama, Daddy is crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:28.96,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:34.34,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:43.35,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:49.73,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:54.32,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:59.99,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:07.46,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:12.67,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:23.39,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:29.23,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:38.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A confidential meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:41.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like they have one\Nevery Friday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.49,0:22:43.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:46.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on it today!
